                  <p>For practitioners with some yoga experience. These classes introduce more complex poses, transitions, and longer holds to deepen your practice.</p>

                  <div class="level-details">
                    <div class="level-detail-item">
                      <h4>What to Expect</h4>
                      <ul>
                        <li>Faster-paced flows and sequences</li>
                        <li>More challenging pose variations</li>
                        <li>Less detailed instruction (assumes basic knowledge)</li>
                        <li>Longer sequences between breaks</li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="level-detail-item">
                      <h4>Recommended For</h4>
                      <ul>
                        <li>Regular practitioners (6+ months experience)</li>
                        <li>Those comfortable with basic poses and alignment</li>
                        <li>Students wanting to deepen their practice</li>
                        <li>Those with good body awareness</li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              {% elif level == "Advanced" %}
                <div class="level-description">
                  <p>Challenging practices for experienced yogis. These classes include advanced postures, complex sequences, and require greater strength and flexibility.</p>

                  <div class="level-details">
                    <div class="level-detail-item">
                      <h4>What to Expect</h4>
                      <ul>
                        <li>Complex arm balances and inversions</li>
                        <li>Deep backbends and forward folds</li>
                        <li>Challenging transitions between poses</li>
                        <li>Minimal instruction (assumes significant experience)</li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>

