                        <li>Dedicated practitioners (2+ years experience)</li>
                        <li>Those with strong body awareness</li>
                        <li>Students with established home practice</li>
                        <li>Those with significant strength and flexibility</li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              {% else %}
