                    <div class="level-detail-item">
                      <h4>What to Expect</h4>
                      <ul>
                        <li>Options for different skill levels</li>
                        <li>Accessible base poses with additional variations</li>
                        <li>Balanced pace with modifications</li>
                        <li>Clear cues for both beginners and advanced students</li>
                      </ul>
